Package nl.tno.stormcv.util.connector

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileConnector
    An interface for connectors to (remote) locations like AWS S3.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClasspathConnector
    A FileConnector implementation to read files from the classpath.
    ConnectorHolder
    Utility class used to maintain a set of FileConnector implementations registered in the StormCVConfig.
    FtpConnector
    A FileConnector implementation used to access FTP sites.
    LocalFileConnector
    A FileConnector implementation used to interact with files on the local file system.
    S3Connector
    A FileConnector implementation used to access AWS S3 buckets.
